{"@class": "com.nd.elearning.sdk.resource.gateway.v5.bean.question.QuestionVo", "original_type": 4, "original_sub_type": "questions", "container_id": "elearning-library_ncet-xedu_080ae380-40bc-4a84-b761-eee39249c878", "id": "0d469620-768c-420c-b0d5-e4e31a1c6a7a", "type": 201, "content": {"preview": {"question_big": "https://r1-ndr.ykt.cbern.com.cn/edu_product/esp/questions/0d469620-768c-420c-b0d5-e4e31a1c6a7a@2.pkg/1772597648393/mainbig.xml.jpg?v=1772597648816", "question_small": "https://r1-ndr.ykt.cbern.com.cn/edu_product/esp/questions/0d469620-768c-420c-b0d5-e4e31a1c6a7a@2.pkg/1772597648393/mainbig.xml.jpg?v=1772597648816"}, "identifier": "0d469620-768c-420c-b0d5-e4e31a1c6a7a", "feedbacks": [{"identifier": "showHint", "sequence": "1", "outcome_identifier": "FEEDBACK", "show_hide": "show", "content": ""}, {"identifier": "showAnswer", "sequence": "1", "outcome_identifier": "FEEDBACK", "show_hide": "show", "content": "<p>&nbsp;正确答案：A</p>\n\n<p>①航母远海训练直接体现维护国家主权和领土完整；</p>\n\n<p>②设立新疆自贸区喀什片区涉及边疆发展和国家安全；</p>\n\n<p>③老旧小区改造属于民生工程，不直接涉及国家核心利益；</p>\n\n<p>④海巡船列编强化南海执法能力直接维护海洋权益。</p>\n"}], "sequnce_number": 1, "description": "<p>（改编）国家核心利益是国家安全的重要保障。下列属于维护我国国家核心利益的有（）</p>\n\n<p>①福建舰航母完成首次远海实战化训练</p>\n\n<p>②国务院批准设立新疆自贸试验区喀什片区</p>\n\n<p>③某市开展老旧小区改造提升居民生活品质</p>\n\n<p>④\"海巡173\"轮正式列编强化南海巡航执法能力</p>\n", "title": "（改编）国家核心利益是国家安全的重要保障。下列属于维护我国国家核心利益的有（）①福建舰航母完成首次远海实战化训练②国务院批准设立新疆自贸试验区喀什片区③某市开展老旧小区改造提升居民生活品质④\"海巡173\"轮正式列编强化南海巡航执法能力", "res_type": "$RE0201", "adaptive": false, "timer": {"timer_type": "sequence"}, "time_dependent": false, "responses": [{"identifier": "RESPONSE_1-1", "sequence": "1-1", "base_type": "identifier", "cardinality": "single", "corrects": ["A"]}], "location": "https://r1-ndr.ykt.cbern.com.cn/edu_product/esp/questions/0d469620-768c-420c-b0d5-e4e31a1c6a7a@2.pkg/item.json?v=1754618728475", "items": [{"min_choices": 0, "attachments": [], "columns": 1, "type": "choice", "choices_list": [], "associable_hotspots": [], "children": [], "hide_answer_area": false, "opti